<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sign in to Monobase</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .signin-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .signin-button:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .expiration {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #fee2e2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .backup-link {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0 16px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .header, .content {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏥 Monobase</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Sign in to your account</h2>
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>

            <p>Use the button below to sign in to your Monobase account ({{email}}). No password needed.</p>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{magicLink}}" class="signin-button">Sign In</a>
            </div>

            <div class="expiration">
                <strong>⏰ Heads up:</strong> This sign-in link is single-use and expires shortly. If it has expired, request a new one from the sign-in page.
            </div>

            <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
            <div class="backup-link">{{magicLink}}</div>

            <div class="security-notice">
                <strong>🔒 Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this link, you can safely ignore this email. Your account stays secure and no one can sign in without this link.
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for trusting Monobase with your service needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Monobase</strong><br>
            Secure • Reliable • Professional Service</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
